---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Portfolio • Senior Frontend Engineer">
  <section class="section">
    <h1>senior frontend engineer.</h1>
    <p class="highlight">building scalable web applications with modern technologies</p>
    <p>
      passionate about creating efficient, maintainable code and exceptional user experiences. 
      specialized in <span class="highlight">react</span>, <span class="highlight">typescript</span>, 
      and <span class="highlight">modern frontend architecture</span>.
    </p>
    <p class="muted">
      currently focused on performance optimization, accessibility, and developer experience improvements.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>recent work</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>enterprise dashboard platform</h3>
      <p>
        led the development of a real-time analytics dashboard serving 50k+ users. 
        implemented micro-frontend architecture with module federation, reducing bundle size by 40%.
      </p>
      <p class="muted">react • typescript • webpack • graphql</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card">
      <h3>design system & component library</h3>
      <p>
        architected and maintained a comprehensive design system adopted across 15+ products. 
        established automated testing, documentation, and release processes.
      </p>
      <p class="muted">storybook • styled-components • jest • chromatic</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>get in touch</h2>
    <p>
      interested in collaboration or have questions about my work? 
      <span class="highlight">let's connect</span>.
    </p>
    <p class="muted">email • linkedin • github</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
